    <item>
      <title>高盛首席执行官所罗门：交易环境正在改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-29/goldman-ceo-solomon-dealmaking-environment-is-improving-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团首席执行官戴维·所罗门 (David Solomon) 讨论了该银行业务的前景，并表示“毫无疑问交易环境正在改善”。他在利雅得沙特旗舰未来投资计划间隙与彭博社的 Joumanna Bercetche 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-29/goldman-ceo-solomon-dealmaking-environment-is-improving-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行奖金池有望追平去年十年高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/hsbc-bonus-pool-on-course-to-match-last-year-s-decade-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司的银行家们预计将分享 2024 年的奖金池，价值至少与去年的约 38 亿美元相当。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/hsbc-bonus-pool-on-course-to-match-last-year-s-decade-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛的所罗门“担心”中东冲突加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/goldman-s-solomon-concerned-about-widening-mideast-conflict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团首席执行官戴维·所罗门对中东地区冲突加剧表示担忧，尽管目前冲突尚未对业务产生重大影响。]]></description>
