    <item>
      <title>波音公司增资 210 亿美元以增强流动性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/boeing-raises-21-billion-in-capital-hike-to-boost-liquidity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司通过扩大股票发行筹集了约 210 亿美元，这是上市公司有史以来规模最大的股票发行之一，旨在增强其资产负债表，避免信用评级被下调至垃圾级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/boeing-raises-21-billion-in-capital-hike-to-boost-liquidity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:17:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大选临近，比特币自 6 月以来首次突破 71,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/bitcoin-btc-tops-70-000-for-first-time-since-june-as-election-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受专用交易所交易基金流入以及对下周美国大选结果的猜测的推动，比特币自 6 月以来首次突破 71,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/bitcoin-btc-tops-70-000-for-first-time-since-june-as-election-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 23:42:18 GMT</pubDate>
